          "elements": [
            {
              "id": "elem00007v",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "icon-box",
              "settings": {
                "title_text": "Crypto Portfolio Compliance & Tax-Ready Books",
                "description_text": "<p style=\"margin-bottom:8px;\"><span style=\"background:#161B2E;color:#6366F1;padding:4px 12px;border-radius:999px;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:2px;\">CRYPTO / DIGITAL ASSETS</span> <span style=\"color:#8B91A0;font-size:13px;margin-left:8px;\">DeFi Protocol Founder — Remote (US-based)</span></p>\n\n<div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr;gap:24px;margin-top:24px;\">\n<div>\n<p style=\"color:#8B91A0;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:8px;\">🎯 THE CHALLENGE</p>\n<p style=\"color:#D8DCE4;font-size:15px;line-height:1.7;\">A founder running a DeFi protocol and personal crypto portfolio had no formal bookkeeping. Over 2,000 transactions across 8 wallets and 3 exchanges were unreconciled. The founder faced a potential IRS inquiry and needed clean, defensible records before tax season.</p>\n</div>\n<div>\n<p style=\"color:#8B91A0;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:8px;\">💡 OUR APPROACH</p>\n<p style=\"color:#D8DCE4;font-size:15px;line-height:1.7;\">We integrated wallet and exchange data into a unified tracking system, applied FIFO cost-basis methodology across all transactions, and reconciled the full transaction history. We then set up ongoing automated categorization rules in QBO for fiat on/off ramps and staking rewards.</p>\n</div>\n<div>\n<p style=\"color:#8B91A0;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:8px;\">📈 THE OUTCOMES</p>\n<ul style=\"list-style:none;padding:0;\"><li style=\"margin-bottom:8px;color:#D8DCE4;font-size:15px;\">✓ 2,000+ transactions reconciled across 8 wallets</li><li style=\"margin-bottom:8px;color:#D8DCE4;font-size:15px;\">✓ Tax-ready P&L and balance sheet delivered 6 weeks before deadline</li><li style=\"margin-bottom:8px;color:#D8DCE4;font-size:15px;\">✓ Automated monthly categorization saving 10+ hours/month</li><li style=\"margin-bottom:8px;color:#D8DCE4;font-size:15px;\">✓ No IRS issues — clean compliance posture established</li></ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"margin-top:24px;padding-top:20px;border-top:1px solid #252B3D;\">\n<a href=\"/contact\" style=\"color:#6366F1;font-weight:600;font-size:14px;\">Get results like these — Book a discovery call →</a>\n</div>",
                "selected_icon": {
                  "value": "fas fa-chart-line",
                  "library": "fa-solid"
                },
                "icon_color": "#6366F1",
                "title_color": "#FFFFFF",
                "title_typography_typography": "custom",
